# Build directory (mandatory)

- **Single build directory:** `_build` (with underscore). Do **not** use `build`.
- Configure: `cmake -S . -B _build ...`
- Build: `cmake --build _build ...`
- Run: `_build\bin\Release\ui_sandbox.exe` or `_build\bin\Debug\ui_sandbox.exe`

If you suggest or run CMake/ctest commands, use `_build` only.

**vcpkg по умолчанию:** triplet **`x64-windows-static`** + **`VCPKG_OVERLAY_PORTS`** = **`toolchain/vcpkg-overlay/ports`** (именно каталог `ports`, не родитель). Overlay `shader-slang`: исходники **с GitHub** (SHA в `ports/shader-slang/portfile.cmake`). См. `CMakePresets.json`. Смена triplet/overlay — пересоздай `_build`.
